1
00:01:26,300 --> 00:01:34,970
[LIVE UP TO YOUR YOUTH]

2
00:01:35,440 --> 00:01:37,850
[Episode 26]

3
00:01:49,479 --> 00:01:51,009
Mom, you're awake.

4
00:01:53,650 --> 00:01:54,430
Your IV drip is almost done.

5
00:01:54,430 --> 00:01:55,630
I'll go get the nurse.

6
00:01:56,060 --> 00:01:56,870
No need.

7
00:01:57,950 --> 00:01:58,870
The nurse will come on rounds

8
00:01:58,870 --> 00:02:00,370
in a while.

9
00:02:01,810 --> 00:02:03,570
Don't run around, rest a bit.

10
00:02:12,060 --> 00:02:12,800
How have you been feeling

11
00:02:12,800 --> 00:02:14,090
mentally lately?

12
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:16,400
Your wound keeps getting infected,

13
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:19,020
and the side effects
of chemotherapy are severe.

14
00:02:19,020 --> 00:02:20,240
I want to consult an expert

15
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:22,100
to see if there are other options.

16
00:02:24,150 --> 00:02:26,079
I know my body.

17
00:02:27,150 --> 00:02:29,550
I'll be healed and
discharged in a few days.

18
00:02:30,900 --> 00:02:31,829
Be a good girl.

19
00:02:33,370 --> 00:02:34,430
Don't fuss over it.

20
00:02:35,370 --> 00:02:36,840
Don't make me worry.

21
00:02:50,900 --> 00:02:51,760
Zhuang Zhuang,

22
00:02:51,960 --> 00:02:53,840
you must have skipped your meal again.

23
00:02:53,840 --> 00:02:55,240
Come, eat while it's hot.

24
00:02:57,180 --> 00:02:58,180
Thank you, Mr. Ye.

25
00:03:00,630 --> 00:03:01,830
Don't worry too much.

26
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:05,240
I still have

27
00:03:05,620 --> 00:03:07,500
friends who can lend us some money.

28
00:03:07,500 --> 00:03:08,780
If all else fails...

29
00:03:09,630 --> 00:03:10,930
Our shop

30
00:03:11,030 --> 00:03:12,490
can be sold for some money.

31
00:03:19,340 --> 00:03:19,800
Over the years,

32
00:03:19,800 --> 00:03:21,079
most of your savings

33
00:03:22,530 --> 00:03:24,079
have been spent on my singing.

34
00:03:24,079 --> 00:03:25,410
That's how it should be.

35
00:03:26,410 --> 00:03:27,140
Your mom just

36
00:03:27,530 --> 00:03:28,960
wants to be by your side.

37
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:30,740
It's no use persuading her.

38
00:03:30,740 --> 00:03:32,270
You need to understand her.

39
00:03:33,960 --> 00:03:34,820
How about this?

40
00:03:35,190 --> 00:03:37,310
I'll go see what the expert says tomorrow.

41
00:03:37,310 --> 00:03:37,870
Okay.

42
00:03:39,850 --> 00:03:41,850
If we really have to sell the shop...

43
00:03:44,690 --> 00:03:46,810
Once our family gets through
this difficult time,

44
00:03:46,810 --> 00:03:48,470
I will definitely buy it back.

45
00:03:49,930 --> 00:03:50,360
Okay.

46
00:03:52,720 --> 00:03:53,310
Eat up.

47
00:04:07,890 --> 00:04:09,910
The surgery went reasonably well.

48
00:04:10,750 --> 00:04:12,430
But for your mother,

49
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:13,920
at her age,

50
00:04:14,460 --> 00:04:16,519
postoperative recovery is crucial.

51
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:18,740
If she doesn't recover well,

52
00:04:19,540 --> 00:04:21,000
it's very easy to relapse.

53
00:04:21,540 --> 00:04:22,540
Given this situation,

54
00:04:22,540 --> 00:04:24,270
will she need another surgery?

55
00:04:25,070 --> 00:04:27,180
Another open-chest surgery is too risky.

56
00:04:27,180 --> 00:04:29,640
We can only treat it
conservatively for now.

57
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:31,540
How about this?

58
00:04:31,570 --> 00:04:32,720
I'll prescribe a medication

59
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:33,850
called interferon.

60
00:04:34,310 --> 00:04:36,290
It is one of the classic drugs

61
00:04:36,330 --> 00:04:37,930
for adjuvant therapy
after tumor chemotherapy

62
00:04:37,930 --> 00:04:39,390
and surgery.

63
00:04:39,830 --> 00:04:40,860
It can effectively

64
00:04:40,860 --> 00:04:42,659
inhibit the spread of the tumor.

65
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:44,460
It's just a bit expensive.

66
00:04:45,010 --> 00:04:46,870
Currently, our hospital's supply

67
00:04:46,870 --> 00:04:47,830
is all imported.

68
00:04:48,570 --> 00:04:49,970
One course of treatment

69
00:04:50,060 --> 00:04:51,060
costs over 4,000.

70
00:04:51,870 --> 00:04:52,700
You should

71
00:04:52,860 --> 00:04:53,420
decide based on

72
00:04:53,420 --> 00:04:54,890
your family's

73
00:04:54,930 --> 00:04:55,920
specific circumstances.

74
00:04:55,920 --> 00:04:56,310
Okay?

75
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:00,720
I understand.

76
00:05:01,370 --> 00:05:03,370
Please prescribe it for me, doctor.

77
00:05:39,560 --> 00:05:41,180
Domestically processed goods.

78
00:05:41,180 --> 00:05:43,770
Russian cowhide is of
particularly high quality.

79
00:05:43,770 --> 00:05:45,130
We can ship the raw materials from Russia

80
00:05:45,130 --> 00:05:47,680
to China for processing before
selling them back to them.

81
00:05:47,680 --> 00:05:49,409
The profit margin is very high.

82
00:05:49,680 --> 00:05:51,500
I'm telling you, it's promising.

83
00:05:51,500 --> 00:05:52,280
Take a look.

84
00:06:01,330 --> 00:06:02,240
Welcome, listeners,

85
00:06:02,240 --> 00:06:03,370
to our station

86
00:06:03,370 --> 00:06:04,330
at the 14th

87
00:06:04,330 --> 00:06:05,500
Youth Singing Competition

88
00:06:05,500 --> 00:06:06,510
finals.

89
00:06:06,930 --> 00:06:07,890
This final

90
00:06:08,010 --> 00:06:09,430
will be broadcast live,

91
00:06:09,570 --> 00:06:10,560
sharing this auditory feast

92
00:06:10,560 --> 00:06:11,880
with the audience.

93
00:06:12,540 --> 00:06:14,380
Alright, the host is now

94
00:06:14,450 --> 00:06:15,500
backstage.

95
00:06:15,570 --> 00:06:16,770
The contestants are making

96
00:06:16,770 --> 00:06:18,300
their final preparations.

97
00:06:41,830 --> 00:06:42,180
Uncle.

98
00:06:42,180 --> 00:06:42,750
Why is your cough

99
00:06:42,750 --> 00:06:43,690
getting worse?

100
00:06:46,620 --> 00:06:47,370
Blood.

101
00:06:47,850 --> 00:06:48,950
You coughed up blood, Uncle.

102
00:06:48,950 --> 00:06:51,280
Let me take you
to the hospital right away.

103
00:06:55,100 --> 00:06:56,360
I have weathered

104
00:06:56,390 --> 00:06:57,270
many storms.

105
00:06:58,010 --> 00:06:59,040
This is just a minor issue.

106
00:06:59,040 --> 00:07:00,170
Why go to a hospital?

107
00:07:00,270 --> 00:07:01,330
Tell me, what is it?

108
00:07:04,890 --> 00:07:07,530
There is a very capable person

109
00:07:07,950 --> 00:07:10,060
who wants to arrange a meeting with you.

110
00:07:10,060 --> 00:07:11,360
Do I need to worry

111
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:13,760
about such a trivial matter?

112
00:07:14,430 --> 00:07:16,800
You have already
learned everything from me.

113
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:19,430
Just unleash your imagination,

114
00:07:19,690 --> 00:07:21,220
let go of your constraints,

115
00:07:21,540 --> 00:07:22,950
and go do it boldly.

116
00:07:25,540 --> 00:07:25,920
Go.

117
00:07:28,750 --> 00:07:29,100
Go.

118
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:41,620
Chu Caiyuan, I have made it

119
00:07:41,620 --> 00:07:42,500
very clear to you.

120
00:07:42,500 --> 00:07:44,170
Please do not call me again,

121
00:07:44,680 --> 00:07:46,680
and don't send anyone to look for me.

122
00:07:47,659 --> 00:07:48,390
Even if you come,

123
00:07:48,390 --> 00:07:49,420
I will not see you.

124
00:08:21,570 --> 00:08:22,370
Ranran.

125
00:08:30,750 --> 00:08:31,270
Mr. Guo,

126
00:08:32,110 --> 00:08:33,860
you're here to bring me things again?

127
00:08:33,860 --> 00:08:35,549
Well, your aunt said

128
00:08:35,549 --> 00:08:38,130
you didn't eat much tonight,

129
00:08:38,250 --> 00:08:39,650
so she made you some soup.

130
00:08:40,789 --> 00:08:41,909
See if you like it.

131
00:08:42,890 --> 00:08:44,120
Come, try it.

132
00:08:44,530 --> 00:08:45,540
Mr. Guo,

133
00:08:45,670 --> 00:08:46,740
tell Auntie

134
00:08:46,770 --> 00:08:47,940
not to trouble herself anymore.

135
00:08:47,940 --> 00:08:49,720
Don't be polite with us.

136
00:08:50,630 --> 00:08:52,700
Your aunt cares about you.

137
00:08:56,080 --> 00:08:57,340
Have a seat, Mr. Guo.

138
00:09:03,460 --> 00:09:04,260
What's wrong?

139
00:09:05,390 --> 00:09:06,620
Your aunt told me

140
00:09:07,240 --> 00:09:08,320
that lately,

141
00:09:08,840 --> 00:09:09,620
you've been

142
00:09:10,100 --> 00:09:11,320
avoiding everyone

143
00:09:11,320 --> 00:09:12,370
and feeling down.

144
00:09:13,270 --> 00:09:15,290
Are you just in a bad mood,

145
00:09:15,290 --> 00:09:16,690
or did something happen?

146
00:09:16,820 --> 00:09:19,100
If something's wrong, tell us.

147
00:09:19,440 --> 00:09:21,100
We'll figure it out together.

148
00:09:22,030 --> 00:09:23,150
I'm fine.

149
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:25,320
Don't worry.

150
00:09:30,370 --> 00:09:31,410
Are you not

151
00:09:31,410 --> 00:09:32,940
filming your show anymore?

152
00:09:33,100 --> 00:09:34,160
I'm done with that.

153
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:35,570
It's all wrapped up?

154
00:09:35,670 --> 00:09:36,750
That's a good thing.

155
00:09:36,750 --> 00:09:38,010
You should be happy.

156
00:09:41,460 --> 00:09:42,100
Mr. Guo,

157
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:45,050
I probably

158
00:09:46,500 --> 00:09:48,580
won't act anymore in the future.

159
00:09:49,700 --> 00:09:51,770
Is it because of that boss?

160
00:09:59,050 --> 00:10:00,150
Have the invitations been sent out?

161
00:10:00,150 --> 00:10:01,390
They've all been sent.

162
00:10:01,390 --> 00:10:02,460
How are the preparations for the banquet?

163
00:10:02,460 --> 00:10:04,790
Everything is arranged as you requested.

164
00:10:05,130 --> 00:10:06,320
Pay attention to the details.

165
00:10:06,320 --> 00:10:08,290
Details often determine everything.

166
00:10:08,290 --> 00:10:10,420
The key to success lies in the details.

167
00:10:10,460 --> 00:10:11,930
Don't, don't pull me.

168
00:10:12,080 --> 00:10:12,810
Chu Caiyuan!

169
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:13,860
You go first.

170
00:10:13,860 --> 00:10:14,320
Get out.

171
00:10:14,440 --> 00:10:15,500
What are you doing?

172
00:10:16,790 --> 00:10:17,720
I'm sorry, Boss.

173
00:10:17,980 --> 00:10:19,110
I couldn't stop him.

174
00:10:19,390 --> 00:10:19,920
Go first.

175
00:10:21,750 --> 00:10:22,410
Who are you?

176
00:10:23,150 --> 00:10:24,550
I'm Shen Ranran's uncle.

177
00:10:26,670 --> 00:10:27,600
What do you want?

178
00:10:27,670 --> 00:10:29,670
She doesn't want to see you anymore.

179
00:10:30,410 --> 00:10:32,340
Stop pestering her.

180
00:10:35,290 --> 00:10:37,150
If you really are Ranran's uncle,

181
00:10:37,320 --> 00:10:38,250
you should know

182
00:10:39,050 --> 00:10:40,780
that this is between the 2 of us,

183
00:10:41,030 --> 00:10:41,550
right?

184
00:10:42,270 --> 00:10:43,930
Then you should also know that

185
00:10:43,940 --> 00:10:45,170
in a matter between 2 people,

186
00:10:45,170 --> 00:10:46,410
when 1 person decides,

187
00:10:46,410 --> 00:10:47,720
it's decided.

188
00:10:51,270 --> 00:10:51,900
Fine.

189
00:10:52,550 --> 00:10:54,030
If this is Ranran's wish,

190
00:10:54,670 --> 00:10:55,360
I agree.

191
00:10:56,480 --> 00:10:57,050
But I must

192
00:10:57,050 --> 00:10:58,510
hear it from her in person.

193
00:10:59,170 --> 00:11:00,300
That's impossible.

194
00:11:01,910 --> 00:11:02,970
If I want to see her,

195
00:11:03,860 --> 00:11:05,060
I have plenty of ways.

196
00:11:08,910 --> 00:11:09,340
Here.

197
00:11:09,960 --> 00:11:12,560
Remember to keep
this medicine refrigerated.

198
00:11:14,460 --> 00:11:15,260
Actually,

199
00:11:15,480 --> 00:11:16,530
our hospital got a batch

200
00:11:16,530 --> 00:11:17,590
of new interferon.

201
00:11:17,600 --> 00:11:19,260
It's domestically produced.

202
00:11:20,620 --> 00:11:21,270
If you're seeing

203
00:11:21,270 --> 00:11:22,550
the specialist for a follow-up later,

204
00:11:22,550 --> 00:11:23,360
ask him

205
00:11:23,510 --> 00:11:25,110
if you can use this medicine.

206
00:11:27,580 --> 00:11:28,290
I see you come to buy medicine

207
00:11:28,290 --> 00:11:29,070
every week,

208
00:11:29,100 --> 00:11:30,220
and it's quite expensive.

209
00:11:30,220 --> 00:11:31,620
This medicine is domestically produced.

210
00:11:31,620 --> 00:11:32,960
If you can use it,

211
00:11:33,000 --> 00:11:34,260
it'll be much cheaper.

212
00:11:34,890 --> 00:11:35,620
However,

213
00:11:35,890 --> 00:11:37,500
our hospital doesn't have much of it,

214
00:11:37,500 --> 00:11:39,290
so you have to find a way
to get it prescribed.

215
00:11:39,290 --> 00:11:40,460
Go ask the specialist

216
00:11:40,460 --> 00:11:42,120
if he can prescribe it for you.

217
00:11:42,740 --> 00:11:43,740
Can I borrow a pen?

218
00:11:43,740 --> 00:11:45,270
I want to write down
the manufacturer's name.

219
00:11:45,270 --> 00:11:46,460
Just take the medicine box.

220
00:11:46,460 --> 00:11:47,410
The box is empty.

221
00:11:49,080 --> 00:11:49,870
Thank you.

222
00:11:53,940 --> 00:11:54,700
Zouwen.

223
00:11:54,820 --> 00:11:55,720
Here's the thing.

224
00:11:55,720 --> 00:11:56,960
My friend is in a lot of debt

225
00:11:56,960 --> 00:11:59,090
and wants to borrow some money from you.

226
00:11:59,090 --> 00:12:00,530
It's a lot, yes.

227
00:12:00,980 --> 00:12:01,840
Well, how much?

228
00:12:02,170 --> 00:12:02,770
300,000.

229
00:12:05,580 --> 00:12:06,200
Wen.

230
00:12:06,200 --> 00:12:07,460
Well, my friend was kidding.

231
00:12:07,460 --> 00:12:08,050
It's a joke.

232
00:12:08,050 --> 00:12:08,550
Sorry.

233
00:12:08,550 --> 00:12:09,340
Sorry to bother you.

234
00:12:09,340 --> 00:12:10,390
I'll treat you to a meal later.

235
00:12:10,390 --> 00:12:11,920
Wish you good fortune. Bye.

236
00:12:12,220 --> 00:12:13,080
300,000?

237
00:12:13,320 --> 00:12:14,910
You asked me to get 300,000 for you?

238
00:12:14,910 --> 00:12:16,510
Do I look like 300,000 to you?

239
00:12:16,870 --> 00:12:17,840
What did you do?

240
00:12:17,870 --> 00:12:19,130
How could you owe 300,000?

241
00:12:19,130 --> 00:12:21,470
I'm not asking to borrow 300,000 from you.

242
00:12:21,940 --> 00:12:23,600
I want to do business with you

243
00:12:23,670 --> 00:12:24,800
to earn 300,000.

244
00:12:24,840 --> 00:12:26,310
I'm in so much debt now.

245
00:12:26,370 --> 00:12:27,150
If I borrow from friends again,

246
00:12:27,150 --> 00:12:27,670
wouldn't that just be

247
00:12:27,670 --> 00:12:29,130
robbing Peter to pay Paul?

248
00:12:30,360 --> 00:12:31,150
Here's the thing.

249
00:12:31,150 --> 00:12:32,360
The business we can do

250
00:12:32,360 --> 00:12:33,500
is nothing more than buying and selling.

251
00:12:33,500 --> 00:12:33,980
Buying and selling can only

252
00:12:33,980 --> 00:12:35,170
make tens of thousands a year.

253
00:12:35,170 --> 00:12:36,770
How many years would it take?

254
00:12:39,860 --> 00:12:40,920
Have you seen this?

255
00:12:45,960 --> 00:12:46,690
Raw cowhide.

256
00:12:49,050 --> 00:12:50,200
Smells like mutton. From Russia?

257
00:12:50,200 --> 00:12:50,580
Yes.

258
00:12:51,000 --> 00:12:51,340
This stuff

259
00:12:51,340 --> 00:12:52,460
is everywhere in Russia.

260
00:12:52,460 --> 00:12:53,000
Yeah.

261
00:12:53,630 --> 00:12:54,130
Because

262
00:12:54,150 --> 00:12:55,810
it's everywhere in Russia,

263
00:12:56,030 --> 00:12:56,840
its price

264
00:12:56,840 --> 00:12:58,520
is a third of that in China.

265
00:12:58,650 --> 00:13:00,310
Two dollars a kilo.

266
00:13:00,630 --> 00:13:01,820
We buy the hide back,

267
00:13:01,820 --> 00:13:03,030
make it into leather shoes and clothes,

268
00:13:03,030 --> 00:13:04,090
and resell it.

269
00:13:04,120 --> 00:13:05,050
I calculated it.

270
00:13:06,000 --> 00:13:08,080
The profit is over 300%.

271
00:13:09,030 --> 00:13:10,530
Your calculation is wrong.

272
00:13:10,530 --> 00:13:12,200
You still need to find a factory

273
00:13:12,200 --> 00:13:13,550
to process and make it.

274
00:13:13,600 --> 00:13:14,790
The factories are all booked now.

275
00:13:14,790 --> 00:13:15,790
We can't get a slot at all.

276
00:13:15,790 --> 00:13:16,990
I've found a factory.

277
00:13:17,270 --> 00:13:19,500
But they are in a similar situation to us.

278
00:13:19,500 --> 00:13:20,320
And what's our situation?

279
00:13:20,320 --> 00:13:21,580
We're short on money.

280
00:13:23,820 --> 00:13:24,650
You've found the factory

281
00:13:24,650 --> 00:13:25,910
and the raw materials.

282
00:13:26,460 --> 00:13:27,480
Then you can do this alone.

283
00:13:27,480 --> 00:13:28,880
You don't need to find me.

284
00:13:28,960 --> 00:13:29,690
That's true.

285
00:13:30,150 --> 00:13:31,950
You've come to the right person.

286
00:13:32,370 --> 00:13:33,780
Find Lucky, get lucky.

287
00:13:34,320 --> 00:13:36,650
We are really suited
for doing business together,

288
00:13:36,650 --> 00:13:36,940
aren't we?

289
00:13:36,940 --> 00:13:38,270
Look at your strong body

290
00:13:38,290 --> 00:13:39,250
and my smart brain.

291
00:13:39,250 --> 00:13:39,820
Right?

292
00:13:39,820 --> 00:13:40,340
No, what do you mean?

293
00:13:40,340 --> 00:13:42,270
My brain isn't smart enough?

294
00:13:42,290 --> 00:13:43,950
It's smart enough. Very good.

295
00:13:44,130 --> 00:13:45,130
Well...

296
00:13:45,320 --> 00:13:46,250
Let's do it.

297
00:13:46,320 --> 00:13:46,920
Yes, deal.

298
00:13:47,740 --> 00:13:49,600
Where are the factory employees?

299
00:13:50,130 --> 00:13:50,700
Wenzhou.

300
00:13:52,390 --> 00:13:53,320
That's a bit far.

301
00:13:54,500 --> 00:13:55,150
Do we have to

302
00:13:55,150 --> 00:13:56,270
go to the factory to have a look?

303
00:13:56,270 --> 00:13:56,870
We have to.

304
00:13:57,080 --> 00:13:58,210
When are we leaving?

305
00:13:58,670 --> 00:13:59,250
The 8th.

306
00:14:02,150 --> 00:14:02,790
Since you're here today,

307
00:14:02,790 --> 00:14:03,940
I must treat you to something.

308
00:14:03,940 --> 00:14:05,010
We have to celebrate.

309
00:14:05,010 --> 00:14:06,470
Let's go. Don't just talk.

310
00:14:06,580 --> 00:14:07,530
Let's go.

311
00:14:07,750 --> 00:14:09,150
What should we eat?

312
00:14:09,790 --> 00:14:10,960
Have you tried the

313
00:14:10,960 --> 00:14:12,000
douzhi downstairs?

314
00:14:12,000 --> 00:14:12,460
Douzhi?

315
00:14:12,510 --> 00:14:13,620
The taste is very authentic.

316
00:14:13,620 --> 00:14:14,240
Forget about the douzhi.

317
00:14:14,240 --> 00:14:15,440
Think it's too cheap?

318
00:14:16,270 --> 00:14:16,930
Wait for me.

319
00:14:17,760 --> 00:14:18,660
[Office Building]

320
00:14:19,750 --> 00:14:22,110
[Office building]

321
00:14:24,720 --> 00:14:28,080
[Oujiang Leather Processing Factory]

322
00:14:33,050 --> 00:14:34,380
Everyone, listen to me.

323
00:14:34,410 --> 00:14:35,840
I didn't run away.

324
00:14:36,670 --> 00:14:38,080
I'm right here.

325
00:14:38,620 --> 00:14:39,740
It's not that I don't want

326
00:14:39,740 --> 00:14:41,050
to pay you.

327
00:14:41,200 --> 00:14:42,010
You all know how little profit

328
00:14:42,010 --> 00:14:43,050
the factory is making.

329
00:14:43,050 --> 00:14:44,580
The machine is also broken.

330
00:14:44,740 --> 00:14:46,670
It costs money to hire someone to fix it.

331
00:14:46,670 --> 00:14:47,550
Just wait until I hire a worker

332
00:14:47,550 --> 00:14:48,610
to fix the machine.

333
00:14:48,650 --> 00:14:50,250
As long as we take the first order

334
00:14:50,250 --> 00:14:50,980
and make some money,

335
00:14:50,980 --> 00:14:52,340
I will deliver the money

336
00:14:52,360 --> 00:14:53,960
door to door in person, okay?

337
00:14:54,000 --> 00:14:55,060
I bow to you all.

338
00:14:55,150 --> 00:14:55,960
Go on back.

339
00:14:56,960 --> 00:14:58,070
One last week.

340
00:14:58,240 --> 00:14:59,220
One last week.

341
00:15:00,340 --> 00:15:01,260
One last week.

342
00:15:01,440 --> 00:15:04,470
[Oujiang Leather Processing Factory]

343
00:15:01,500 --> 00:15:03,440
Everyone, please wait at home for now.

344
00:15:03,440 --> 00:15:04,250
Please head back.

345
00:15:04,250 --> 00:15:04,840
Thank you.

346
00:15:04,840 --> 00:15:05,570
Wait at home.

347
00:15:05,770 --> 00:15:07,100
You will get your money.

348
00:15:11,000 --> 00:15:11,580
Well...

349
00:15:12,180 --> 00:15:14,360
[Oujiang Leather Processing Factory]

350
00:15:16,250 --> 00:15:18,270
That's my bag. There's no money inside.

351
00:15:18,270 --> 00:15:19,200
What's going on?

352
00:15:19,550 --> 00:15:21,320
Are you collecting debts
or taking my life?

353
00:15:21,320 --> 00:15:22,530
Neither.

354
00:15:22,750 --> 00:15:24,290
We are from Beijing.

355
00:15:24,480 --> 00:15:25,410
Here to save you.

356
00:15:26,320 --> 00:15:27,120
Save me?

357
00:15:27,790 --> 00:15:28,200
Yes.

358
00:15:28,740 --> 00:15:30,540
We have an order for you.

359
00:15:30,630 --> 00:15:31,160
An order?

360
00:15:34,550 --> 00:15:36,010
Did you bring the deposit?

361
00:15:37,220 --> 00:15:38,700
We have no cash, but...

362
00:15:40,320 --> 00:15:41,850
We have a way to make it work.

363
00:15:45,700 --> 00:15:46,560
Take a look.

364
00:15:46,790 --> 00:15:48,130
This is Vladivostok cowhide,

365
00:15:48,130 --> 00:15:50,670
quick-frozen at minus 40 degrees.

366
00:15:51,550 --> 00:15:53,200
Look at the pores inside.

367
00:15:53,200 --> 00:15:55,130
They are finer than a needle's eye.

368
00:15:55,960 --> 00:15:56,890
It's good stuff.

369
00:16:00,080 --> 00:16:01,030
Imported material?

370
00:16:01,030 --> 00:16:01,440
Right.

371
00:16:02,390 --> 00:16:03,250
Export orders?

372
00:16:03,250 --> 00:16:03,780
Exactly.

373
00:16:04,980 --> 00:16:06,910
I've seen too much of this. Go back.

374
00:16:07,350 --> 00:16:08,560
Wait a minute.

375
00:16:09,000 --> 00:16:10,890
Don't just run away. Seriously.

376
00:16:11,270 --> 00:16:12,940
What's up with you guys?

377
00:16:13,740 --> 00:16:15,700
Factory 2 ordered
Russian material last year.

378
00:16:15,700 --> 00:16:17,500
When the truck came back
and they uncovered it,

379
00:16:17,500 --> 00:16:19,360
it was all rotten like moldy tofu.

380
00:16:19,840 --> 00:16:20,890
The middleman dealers must have

381
00:16:20,890 --> 00:16:22,600
splashed salt water to add weight.

382
00:16:22,600 --> 00:16:24,130
But you've seen our leather.

383
00:16:24,130 --> 00:16:25,390
This is just the cowhide.

384
00:16:25,390 --> 00:16:26,850
We also have buffalo hide.

385
00:16:27,080 --> 00:16:27,750
How about this?

386
00:16:27,750 --> 00:16:29,330
When you inspect the goods,

387
00:16:29,750 --> 00:16:31,130
if there is even 1 bad piece of leather,

388
00:16:31,130 --> 00:16:32,750
we'll call it quits, okay?

389
00:16:34,980 --> 00:16:36,510
How should I put this to you?

390
00:16:38,440 --> 00:16:39,200
Young man.

391
00:16:39,960 --> 00:16:41,250
From your posture,

392
00:16:41,620 --> 00:16:43,950
this is your first time doing this, right?

393
00:16:44,250 --> 00:16:44,750
Yes.

394
00:16:45,220 --> 00:16:46,350
Let me tell you this.

395
00:16:46,840 --> 00:16:49,100
These export orders are not that simple.

396
00:16:49,170 --> 00:16:50,930
When your goods arrive there,

397
00:16:51,170 --> 00:16:52,740
you are no longer in control.

398
00:16:52,740 --> 00:16:54,130
Let's not even talk about the payment.

399
00:16:54,130 --> 00:16:56,320
It'd be good enough if you could come back

400
00:16:56,320 --> 00:16:57,050
in one piece.

401
00:16:57,650 --> 00:16:59,170
So many people have failed there.

402
00:16:59,170 --> 00:16:59,770
What?

403
00:17:00,370 --> 00:17:02,830
You 2 still want to
throw yourselves into it?

404
00:17:04,000 --> 00:17:05,270
Well, my old friend.

405
00:17:05,270 --> 00:17:06,829
You don't know who I am.

406
00:17:07,069 --> 00:17:07,880
My name is Lucky Ma.

407
00:17:07,880 --> 00:17:08,940
I do trade in Russia

408
00:17:08,940 --> 00:17:09,680
all year round.

409
00:17:09,680 --> 00:17:11,329
Look at me, I'm perfectly fine, aren't I?

410
00:17:11,329 --> 00:17:12,869
And let me tell you,

411
00:17:12,920 --> 00:17:13,910
I keep my word.

412
00:17:13,930 --> 00:17:15,200
If I say I'll pay you,
I will definitely pay you.

413
00:17:15,200 --> 00:17:16,230
My words are solid like nails.

414
00:17:16,230 --> 00:17:17,589
Like the date pits Qiu Qianchi

415
00:17:17,589 --> 00:17:18,790
spat out in the story.

416
00:17:18,980 --> 00:17:19,380
Right?

417
00:17:19,609 --> 00:17:20,510
Just trust me.

418
00:17:20,530 --> 00:17:22,190
If not, we can sign a contract.

419
00:17:22,420 --> 00:17:22,810
I thought

420
00:17:22,810 --> 00:17:24,720
you were going to spit date pits at me.

421
00:17:24,720 --> 00:17:26,030
We heard that in 1983,

422
00:17:26,380 --> 00:17:27,790
this factory was not doing well.

423
00:17:27,790 --> 00:17:29,050
You were the youngest factory director

424
00:17:29,050 --> 00:17:30,110
at the time,

425
00:17:30,330 --> 00:17:31,730
and you were an outsider.

426
00:17:31,830 --> 00:17:33,420
You led everyone together,

427
00:17:33,530 --> 00:17:34,420
worked 3 shifts a day,

428
00:17:34,420 --> 00:17:36,180
and relied on those old machines.

429
00:17:36,180 --> 00:17:36,940
Despite that, you completed

430
00:17:36,940 --> 00:17:38,750
your first
foreign trade order, didn't you?

431
00:17:38,750 --> 00:17:39,810
Back then, everyone

432
00:17:39,810 --> 00:17:40,810
got a dividend.

433
00:17:41,440 --> 00:17:43,330
Don't you want to rely on
foreign trade orders

434
00:17:43,330 --> 00:17:44,790
to save the factory again?

435
00:17:45,830 --> 00:17:46,720
When you get to a place,

436
00:17:45,990 --> 00:17:49,340
[Old Wenzhou Specialty Snack Shop]

437
00:17:46,750 --> 00:17:47,330
you have to eat

438
00:17:47,330 --> 00:17:48,550
their local food.

439
00:17:48,880 --> 00:17:50,300
This is called "When in Rome,
do as the Romans do,"

440
00:17:50,300 --> 00:17:51,060
you know?

441
00:17:51,140 --> 00:17:52,610
Like these Wenzhou fish balls

442
00:17:52,610 --> 00:17:53,330
and this dried rice noodle,

443
00:17:53,330 --> 00:17:54,400
they are all very famous.

444
00:17:54,400 --> 00:17:55,290
What we're eating now

445
00:17:55,290 --> 00:17:56,590
is called pork offal noodles.

446
00:17:56,590 --> 00:17:57,830
Here are your pork offal noodles.

447
00:17:57,830 --> 00:17:58,960
-Thank you.
-Enjoy.

448
00:17:59,290 --> 00:18:00,510
Thank you.

449
00:18:01,290 --> 00:18:02,030
Pork offal noodles.

450
00:18:02,030 --> 00:18:02,480
Right.

451
00:18:03,110 --> 00:18:04,110
It's not dirty at all.

452
00:18:04,110 --> 00:18:05,240
It's as clean as I am.

453
00:18:07,010 --> 00:18:07,820
Oh, right.

454
00:18:07,960 --> 00:18:09,120
About the factory equipment,

455
00:18:09,120 --> 00:18:10,180
we both took a look.

456
00:18:13,620 --> 00:18:14,350
It's not bad.

457
00:18:15,240 --> 00:18:16,270
Their factory equipment

458
00:18:16,270 --> 00:18:17,870
is really good.

459
00:18:19,590 --> 00:18:20,220
You can tell that

460
00:18:20,220 --> 00:18:21,780
they spent a lot of money
on it in the early years.

461
00:18:21,780 --> 00:18:23,110
But the problem is that
the machines are abandoned,

462
00:18:23,110 --> 00:18:23,850
and there are no workers.

463
00:18:23,850 --> 00:18:24,290
So we need

464
00:18:24,290 --> 00:18:26,020
a solution for those problems.

465
00:18:26,180 --> 00:18:26,940
I heard from Liangliang that

466
00:18:26,940 --> 00:18:28,880
when you were acting
as a middleman before,

467
00:18:28,880 --> 00:18:29,900
you knew a key technical staff member

468
00:18:29,900 --> 00:18:30,960
from some factory.

469
00:18:31,010 --> 00:18:31,790
What was the name of that factory again?

470
00:18:31,790 --> 00:18:33,310
The factory was called...

471
00:18:33,660 --> 00:18:34,750
Yes. That person's surname is Pan.

472
00:18:34,750 --> 00:18:37,290
His name is Pan... Pan...

473
00:18:37,980 --> 00:18:39,300
Pan Shi or something.

474
00:18:39,400 --> 00:18:41,460
-Mr. Pan. The chief.
-Yes, the chief.

475
00:18:42,010 --> 00:18:43,220
Can you invite him over?

476
00:18:43,220 --> 00:18:44,080
I probably can.

477
00:18:44,200 --> 00:18:45,200
I'll give it a try.

478
00:18:45,240 --> 00:18:46,900
Actually, he really hates businessmen.

479
00:18:46,900 --> 00:18:47,640
After the businessmen

480
00:18:47,640 --> 00:18:48,570
went to his place,

481
00:18:48,570 --> 00:18:49,960
they fired all his colleagues

482
00:18:49,960 --> 00:18:51,270
and only kept the technical team,

483
00:18:51,270 --> 00:18:51,880
making it seem like

484
00:18:51,880 --> 00:18:53,240
the team had betrayed the masses.

485
00:18:53,240 --> 00:18:54,300
That's great.

486
00:18:54,460 --> 00:18:56,270
Then I'll leave this to you, Jun.

487
00:18:56,680 --> 00:18:58,030
As for the workers,

488
00:18:58,420 --> 00:18:59,620
that will cost money.

489
00:18:59,660 --> 00:19:01,900
I'll go back to Beijing
and figure out a way.

490
00:19:01,900 --> 00:19:03,430
Look at what you're saying.

491
00:19:03,570 --> 00:19:04,940
You're leaving this to me?

492
00:19:04,940 --> 00:19:06,090
You really act like

493
00:19:06,090 --> 00:19:06,890
a big boss now.

494
00:19:07,240 --> 00:19:07,700
I feel like

495
00:19:07,700 --> 00:19:09,440
you're more like a businessman than I am.

496
00:19:09,440 --> 00:19:10,500
No.

497
00:19:10,850 --> 00:19:12,900
Only you can get this done, Jun.

498
00:19:13,140 --> 00:19:15,670
If it were me,
I wouldn't be able to invite him.

499
00:19:16,570 --> 00:19:17,420
To be honest, I really think

500
00:19:17,420 --> 00:19:19,180
you're smarter than Liangliang.

501
00:19:19,180 --> 00:19:19,740
Liangliang and I

502
00:19:19,740 --> 00:19:20,720
are just not compatible
for making money.

503
00:19:20,720 --> 00:19:21,140
Why?

504
00:19:21,180 --> 00:19:21,720
I'm Mr. Lucky,

505
00:19:21,720 --> 00:19:22,480
and he's Liangliang.

506
00:19:22,480 --> 00:19:23,350
Listen to the names.

507
00:19:23,350 --> 00:19:24,440
"Lucky Liang" sounds like

508
00:19:24,440 --> 00:19:25,460
"Luck has gone cold" instead.

509
00:19:25,460 --> 00:19:26,220
We are different.

510
00:19:26,220 --> 00:19:27,140
Your name means victory.

511
00:19:27,140 --> 00:19:28,500
So we're Lucky and Victory, right?

512
00:19:28,500 --> 00:19:29,380
It sounds auspicious.

513
00:19:29,380 --> 00:19:30,240
Lucky Victory.

514
00:19:30,680 --> 00:19:31,780
And I think Wenzhou

515
00:19:31,900 --> 00:19:32,850
is a pretty good place.

516
00:19:32,850 --> 00:19:33,910
It gathers wealth.

517
00:19:35,160 --> 00:19:35,460
Yes.

518
00:19:35,460 --> 00:19:37,000
I think the address is from Huzhou.

519
00:19:37,000 --> 00:19:38,050
Can you ask for me?

520
00:19:39,290 --> 00:19:39,750
Okay.

521
00:19:40,400 --> 00:19:42,660
I'll definitely find a way to ask for you.

522
00:19:42,740 --> 00:19:43,380
Zhuang,

523
00:19:44,610 --> 00:19:45,680
are you alright?

524
00:19:45,740 --> 00:19:46,380
I'm fine.

525
00:19:47,330 --> 00:19:48,390
Are you doing okay?

526
00:19:48,570 --> 00:19:49,500
I'm doing great.

527
00:19:50,160 --> 00:19:51,830
Zhuang, if anything really happens,

528
00:19:51,830 --> 00:19:53,240
you must tell me.

529
00:19:53,590 --> 00:19:54,900
We can figure it out together.

530
00:19:54,900 --> 00:19:56,560
Don't worry, I'm really fine.

531
00:19:58,890 --> 00:20:00,420
About me calling you,

532
00:20:00,570 --> 00:20:01,720
don't tell Xu, okay?

533
00:20:02,510 --> 00:20:04,480
What's wrong? Did you two fight?

534
00:20:04,750 --> 00:20:05,330
No.

535
00:20:06,140 --> 00:20:07,270
Just reminding you.

536
00:20:07,570 --> 00:20:08,500
I'll hang up now.

537
00:20:24,650 --> 00:20:26,340
I hear you, I hear you.

538
00:20:26,680 --> 00:20:27,510
Let me think about

539
00:20:27,510 --> 00:20:28,670
how to tell him.

540
00:20:30,980 --> 00:20:31,880
Two minutes

541
00:20:31,880 --> 00:20:32,610
are almost up.

542
00:20:32,610 --> 00:20:33,970
I'm hanging up.

543
00:21:09,250 --> 00:21:10,780
What's the meaning of this?

544
00:21:12,590 --> 00:21:13,420
I gave it all to you.

545
00:21:13,420 --> 00:21:14,550
Here's another 500.

546
00:21:17,000 --> 00:21:18,160
Don't mind the smell.

547
00:21:18,160 --> 00:21:20,680
Seriously, what's the meaning of this?

548
00:21:21,530 --> 00:21:23,700
Liangliang called me

549
00:21:23,700 --> 00:21:24,530
and said...

550
00:21:26,400 --> 00:21:28,260
Let me think about how to tell you.

551
00:21:28,790 --> 00:21:30,390
Let me organize my thoughts.

552
00:21:31,520 --> 00:21:33,290
Zhuang Zhuang and you...

553
00:21:33,940 --> 00:21:36,070
Zhuang Zhuang is from Wenzhou, right?

554
00:21:40,500 --> 00:21:42,030
Have you contacted her recently?

555
00:21:42,030 --> 00:21:42,590
No.

556
00:21:43,980 --> 00:21:44,820
Why not?

557
00:21:45,030 --> 00:21:46,830
She doesn't want me to.

558
00:21:47,950 --> 00:21:49,460
You sure care a lot about this.

559
00:21:49,460 --> 00:21:50,700
Okay, if that's your attitude,

560
00:21:50,700 --> 00:21:52,850
then I'll just tell you.

561
00:21:53,720 --> 00:21:54,420
Liangliang called.

562
00:21:54,420 --> 00:21:55,530
We were talking about something else,

563
00:21:55,530 --> 00:21:56,290
and he happened to mention

564
00:21:56,290 --> 00:21:58,690
that Zhuang Zhuang was looking for Ranran.

565
00:21:59,480 --> 00:22:01,170
She called Ranran to ask

566
00:22:01,310 --> 00:22:03,170
about a pharmaceutical factory.

567
00:22:03,770 --> 00:22:05,500
What pharmaceutical factory?

568
00:22:06,240 --> 00:22:06,970
Interferon.

569
00:22:08,460 --> 00:22:10,180
What is an interferon?

570
00:22:12,400 --> 00:22:13,380
Well...

571
00:22:15,700 --> 00:22:16,480
If I tell you,

572
00:22:16,480 --> 00:22:17,440
don't get mad.

573
00:22:18,330 --> 00:22:19,380
Then don't tell me.

574
00:22:19,380 --> 00:22:20,050
Don't tell me.

575
00:22:20,050 --> 00:22:20,940
How can I not tell you?

576
00:22:20,940 --> 00:22:21,680
I'm your bro.

577
00:22:22,380 --> 00:22:24,110
Shouldn't I comfort you first?

578
00:22:25,550 --> 00:22:26,660
Interferon is...

579
00:22:27,500 --> 00:22:28,830
You know cancer, right?

580
00:22:29,240 --> 00:22:30,430
Interferon is

581
00:22:30,740 --> 00:22:32,140
an adjuvant therapy drug

582
00:22:32,240 --> 00:22:34,300
for post-surgery cancer treatment.

583
00:22:39,180 --> 00:22:39,640
Money.

584
00:22:39,640 --> 00:22:40,630
Take the money.

585
00:22:40,740 --> 00:22:41,600
Take the money.

586
00:22:42,090 --> 00:22:42,770
Be careful.

587
00:22:42,770 --> 00:22:44,430
Let me know if it's not enough.

588
00:23:29,810 --> 00:23:30,950
Give me a cabbage.

589
00:23:31,070 --> 00:23:31,720
Cabbage.

590
00:23:34,730 --> 00:23:36,050
And a bit of this vegetable too.

591
00:23:36,050 --> 00:23:36,530
Okay.

592
00:23:37,050 --> 00:23:37,910
Help yourself.

593
00:23:38,310 --> 00:23:39,040
Here's a bag.

594
00:23:50,610 --> 00:23:51,370
Eight taels.

595
00:24:01,500 --> 00:24:02,360
Zhuang Zhuang.

596
00:24:34,090 --> 00:24:35,020
Long time no see.

597
00:24:40,610 --> 00:24:41,410
How are you?

598
00:24:58,750 --> 00:25:00,010
Why are you in Wenzhou?

599
00:25:01,760 --> 00:25:02,750
Xiaojun and I came here

600
00:25:02,750 --> 00:25:03,940
to do some business.

601
00:25:07,310 --> 00:25:09,240
Are you not making movies anymore?

602
00:25:10,500 --> 00:25:11,720
Movie production cycles are long,

603
00:25:11,720 --> 00:25:13,110
and there's post-production to wait for.

604
00:25:13,110 --> 00:25:14,180
I was just thinking

605
00:25:14,660 --> 00:25:16,460
of making some money in between.

606
00:25:18,460 --> 00:25:19,190
That's good.

607
00:25:19,290 --> 00:25:20,020
That's good.

608
00:25:21,240 --> 00:25:22,170
Is it going well?

609
00:25:22,780 --> 00:25:24,580
Very well.

610
00:25:25,400 --> 00:25:26,740
It's just that the factory I found

611
00:25:26,740 --> 00:25:28,670
doesn't have the best conditions.

612
00:25:29,290 --> 00:25:30,550
We can't get enough workers.

613
00:25:30,550 --> 00:25:31,240
So I thought

614
00:25:31,250 --> 00:25:33,010
I'd go back to Beijing
to figure something out.

615
00:25:33,010 --> 00:25:34,140
Do you need any help?

616
00:25:40,960 --> 00:25:41,940
I mean,

617
00:25:42,440 --> 00:25:43,210
my uncle

618
00:25:43,570 --> 00:25:44,220
is a veteran worker

619
00:25:44,220 --> 00:25:45,820
at the textile factory here.

620
00:25:47,090 --> 00:25:48,960
He knows some people

621
00:25:48,960 --> 00:25:50,760
at the leather and cotton mills.

622
00:25:59,490 --> 00:26:00,930
If you need any help,

623
00:26:01,110 --> 00:26:02,040
just let me know.

624
00:26:04,940 --> 00:26:05,820
Can I

625
00:26:06,200 --> 00:26:07,200
go with you later?

626
00:26:14,810 --> 00:26:16,470
Your mother helped me before.

627
00:26:16,840 --> 00:26:18,030
I want to go see her.

628
00:26:24,420 --> 00:26:25,090
Okay.

629
00:26:39,750 --> 00:26:41,790
From your voice on the phone,

630
00:26:42,200 --> 00:26:43,110
I thought

631
00:26:43,380 --> 00:26:44,910
you must be very energetic.

632
00:26:46,290 --> 00:26:47,150
I didn't expect

633
00:26:47,570 --> 00:26:49,210
you'd be even more handsome

634
00:26:49,770 --> 00:26:50,790
than I imagined.

635
00:26:53,140 --> 00:26:53,680
Auntie,

636
00:26:54,420 --> 00:26:56,420
I should have come to see you sooner.

637
00:26:56,940 --> 00:26:59,070
But I've been running around for work,

638
00:26:59,070 --> 00:27:00,380
and I've been so busy.

639
00:27:01,070 --> 00:27:02,660
But you look very well.

640
00:27:03,090 --> 00:27:03,850
Auntie, you must be

641
00:27:03,850 --> 00:27:05,250
recovering well, right?

642
00:27:05,500 --> 00:27:06,900
If you feel unwell anywhere,

643
00:27:06,900 --> 00:27:07,630
just tell me.

644
00:27:07,750 --> 00:27:08,810
When I go back to Beijing this time,

645
00:27:08,810 --> 00:27:09,790
I'll go find some experts

646
00:27:09,790 --> 00:27:10,520
and ask them.

647
00:27:10,790 --> 00:27:11,900
No need.

648
00:27:12,400 --> 00:27:13,460
I'm fine now.

649
00:27:13,530 --> 00:27:14,570
It's just that Zhuang Zhuang

650
00:27:14,570 --> 00:27:16,110
won't let me leave the hospital.

651
00:27:16,110 --> 00:27:17,620
Look how bored I am.

652
00:27:18,110 --> 00:27:21,150
I can only knit to pass the time.

653
00:27:21,510 --> 00:27:23,370
This is delicate craftsmanship.

654
00:27:23,510 --> 00:27:25,090
And it helps you calm your mind.

655
00:27:25,090 --> 00:27:26,090
It's good for you.

656
00:27:29,570 --> 00:27:30,980
It's just that lately,

657
00:27:32,570 --> 00:27:34,370
it's been hard on Zhuang Zhuang.

658
00:27:35,880 --> 00:27:37,140
She even missed

659
00:27:37,140 --> 00:27:39,420
the singing competition
she was longing for

660
00:27:39,420 --> 00:27:41,420
to stay by my side and take care of me.

661
00:27:41,610 --> 00:27:42,200
Auntie,

662
00:27:42,610 --> 00:27:43,990
you can't say that.

663
00:27:44,380 --> 00:27:46,040
Zhuang Zhuang always tells me

664
00:27:46,050 --> 00:27:47,580
her biggest regret is

665
00:27:47,790 --> 00:27:49,420
not being able to be by your side.

666
00:27:49,420 --> 00:27:50,250
When we talked on the phone
a couple of days ago,

667
00:27:50,250 --> 00:27:51,250
she told me again.

668
00:27:51,400 --> 00:27:51,960
She said

669
00:27:52,010 --> 00:27:53,330
being by your side these days

670
00:27:53,330 --> 00:27:54,930
makes her feel very at peace.

671
00:27:55,240 --> 00:27:56,620
You shouldn't let
your imagination run wild.

672
00:27:56,620 --> 00:27:58,110
You must focus on recovering.

673
00:27:58,110 --> 00:27:59,070
Okay.

674
00:28:02,220 --> 00:28:02,820
By the way,

675
00:28:03,240 --> 00:28:05,480
how many days are you staying here?

676
00:28:05,980 --> 00:28:07,340
Zhuang Zhuang told me

677
00:28:07,690 --> 00:28:09,890
that you really love our southern food.

678
00:28:10,460 --> 00:28:12,760
The crabs are in season right now.

679
00:28:13,070 --> 00:28:15,110
When I am discharged in a few days,

680
00:28:16,660 --> 00:28:19,390
I'd like to invite you home for a meal.

681
00:28:22,000 --> 00:28:22,610
Auntie,

682
00:28:23,090 --> 00:28:24,640
there might not be a chance this time.

683
00:28:24,640 --> 00:28:26,370
I'm leaving in a couple of days.

684
00:28:27,660 --> 00:28:28,610
Next month,

685
00:28:28,960 --> 00:28:30,620
I'll come to see you again.

686
00:28:30,900 --> 00:28:32,180
You can cook yourself then

687
00:28:32,180 --> 00:28:33,460
and show off your skills.

688
00:28:33,460 --> 00:28:35,940
Zhuang Zhuang has been
tempting me for a long time, too.

689
00:28:35,940 --> 00:28:36,560
Okay.

690
00:28:36,640 --> 00:28:38,180
Since we've met,

691
00:28:38,480 --> 00:28:39,960
let Zhuang Zhuang take you

692
00:28:40,000 --> 00:28:41,930
to the old street to eat something.

693
00:28:42,010 --> 00:28:42,870
Zhuang Zhuang,

694
00:28:43,010 --> 00:28:45,500
take Shengli to eat drunken shrimp.

695
00:28:46,940 --> 00:28:49,130
I don't know if you'll be used to it.

696
00:28:49,180 --> 00:28:50,540
I'll be fine.

697
00:28:50,850 --> 00:28:52,010
Drunken shrimp, right?

698
00:28:52,010 --> 00:28:53,070
I'm very used to it.

699
00:28:54,180 --> 00:28:56,190
Zhuang Zhuang's always testing me,

700
00:28:56,310 --> 00:28:57,580
so I'm very used to it.

701
00:28:59,750 --> 00:29:00,310
Alright.

702
00:29:01,030 --> 00:29:02,050
Rest a little longer.

703
00:29:02,050 --> 00:29:03,240
I'll take him to eat.

704
00:29:03,660 --> 00:29:04,140
Okay.

705
00:29:04,200 --> 00:29:06,010
Then take him to the old street

706
00:29:06,110 --> 00:29:08,310
and have some of our local specialties.

707
00:29:08,310 --> 00:29:09,200
Eat more.

708
00:29:09,400 --> 00:29:10,350
Order a bit more.

709
00:29:10,370 --> 00:29:11,130
Don't worry.

710
00:29:12,900 --> 00:29:14,160
I'll go tell the nurse.

711
00:29:15,250 --> 00:29:16,140
Go ahead.

712
00:29:16,180 --> 00:29:17,780
Don't worry about me. Hurry.

713
00:29:32,030 --> 00:29:32,700
Auntie,

714
00:29:34,090 --> 00:29:36,330
try hard to eat and sleep well.

715
00:29:37,090 --> 00:29:38,950
Don't think about anything else.

716
00:29:39,810 --> 00:29:41,440
Zhuang Zhuang is used to carrying

717
00:29:41,440 --> 00:29:43,300
everything on her own shoulders.

718
00:29:43,310 --> 00:29:44,970
That's just her personality.

719
00:29:45,510 --> 00:29:46,440
But don't worry.

720
00:29:46,980 --> 00:29:47,850
From now on,

721
00:29:48,570 --> 00:29:49,900
I will carry it with her.

722
00:29:56,090 --> 00:29:57,050
I won't worry.

723
00:30:17,810 --> 00:30:19,820
I see that Auntie's mental state

724
00:30:19,920 --> 00:30:20,720
is quite good.

725
00:30:22,960 --> 00:30:24,220
The surgery went well.

726
00:30:25,030 --> 00:30:26,870
Now we'll see how the recovery goes.

727
00:30:26,870 --> 00:30:30,660
[Hotel]

728
00:30:35,750 --> 00:30:38,280
The old street
my mom mentioned is just ahead.

729
00:30:43,790 --> 00:30:44,650
Zhuang Zhuang.

730
00:30:56,070 --> 00:30:56,930
Zhuang Zhuang.

731
00:30:59,660 --> 00:31:00,300
I'm sorry.

732
00:31:03,420 --> 00:31:04,480
Back then,

733
00:31:04,880 --> 00:31:07,480
I thought you might have
run into some trouble,

734
00:31:07,920 --> 00:31:09,380
but I really didn't expect

735
00:31:09,440 --> 00:31:11,700
you'd have to face a situation like this.

736
00:31:11,830 --> 00:31:13,290
But thinking about it now,

737
00:31:13,750 --> 00:31:15,290
I even forced you to

738
00:31:15,750 --> 00:31:17,350
participate in the singing competition.

739
00:31:17,350 --> 00:31:18,800
Without realizing it,

740
00:31:18,850 --> 00:31:20,290
I made you more stressed.

741
00:31:22,590 --> 00:31:23,480
I'm sorry.

742
00:31:25,440 --> 00:31:26,570
It's not your fault.

743
00:31:28,240 --> 00:31:29,770
I didn't tell you in time.

744
00:31:39,290 --> 00:31:40,090
I only brought

745
00:31:40,110 --> 00:31:41,910
this much cash with me this time.

746
00:31:42,010 --> 00:31:43,720
I didn't bring my bankbook either.

747
00:31:43,720 --> 00:31:46,450
I'll transfer you more
when I get back to Beijing.

748
00:31:52,660 --> 00:31:53,590
I knew

749
00:31:54,740 --> 00:31:56,740
you definitely wouldn't accept it.

750
00:31:59,220 --> 00:32:00,870
We know each other too well.

751
00:32:05,140 --> 00:32:06,200
But think about it.

752
00:32:06,530 --> 00:32:07,250
If

753
00:32:08,790 --> 00:32:10,360
I were the one in trouble,

754
00:32:11,090 --> 00:32:12,270
would you help me?

755
00:32:17,790 --> 00:32:19,430
We're of the same age,

756
00:32:20,050 --> 00:32:21,450
and we both have parents.

757
00:32:22,000 --> 00:32:23,000
Don't be stubborn

758
00:32:28,000 --> 00:32:29,550
with me about this.

759
00:32:31,110 --> 00:32:32,880
Auntie's health comes first.

760
00:32:47,380 --> 00:32:48,050
Thank you.

761
00:32:49,050 --> 00:32:49,900
It's nothing.

762
00:32:56,740 --> 00:32:57,820
How long are you

763
00:32:57,850 --> 00:32:58,940
staying this time?

764
00:32:59,510 --> 00:33:01,770
I'm leaving the morning after tomorrow.

765
00:33:04,070 --> 00:33:04,950
One more thing.

766
00:33:06,240 --> 00:33:07,100
Zhuang Zhuang,

767
00:33:07,980 --> 00:33:10,240
no matter what happens to you from now on,

768
00:33:10,660 --> 00:33:11,810
you must tell me,

769
00:33:13,680 --> 00:33:14,420
okay?

770
00:33:26,660 --> 00:33:28,110
Let's go get something to eat.

771
00:33:28,110 --> 00:33:28,810
No need.

772
00:33:29,790 --> 00:33:30,460
It's so late.

773
00:33:30,460 --> 00:33:31,790
You've had a long day at the hospital.

774
00:33:31,790 --> 00:33:32,920
Let me walk you home.

775
00:33:35,030 --> 00:33:36,430
My house is right nearby.

776
00:33:39,810 --> 00:33:40,330
Okay.

777
00:33:41,570 --> 00:33:42,970
I'll be heading back now.

778
00:33:50,140 --> 00:33:51,600
Zhuang Zhuang, don't cry.

779
00:33:52,010 --> 00:33:52,970
Everything

780
00:33:53,000 --> 00:33:54,440
is moving in a good direction now,

781
00:33:54,440 --> 00:33:55,060
isn't it?

782
00:33:56,140 --> 00:33:58,010
Okay, then I'll be going.

783
00:34:42,360 --> 00:34:42,889
Xiaobao.

784
00:34:43,260 --> 00:34:44,010
Sis Ranran,

785
00:34:44,340 --> 00:34:46,540
my mother made this especially for you.

786
00:34:48,920 --> 00:34:50,719
Smell it. Doesn't it smell good?

787
00:34:57,510 --> 00:34:58,650
Sis, what's wrong?

788
00:35:00,730 --> 00:35:01,440
I'm fine.

789
00:35:02,000 --> 00:35:03,800
Please thank your mother for me.

790
00:35:04,730 --> 00:35:05,230
Okay.

791
00:35:05,960 --> 00:35:07,090
Are you really okay?

792
00:35:21,350 --> 00:35:22,080
There.

793
00:35:23,670 --> 00:35:24,830
For the growing boy.

794
00:35:25,550 --> 00:35:26,280
You're back.

795
00:35:27,170 --> 00:35:28,800
Come, eat.

796
00:35:35,010 --> 00:35:36,170
Did she like it?

797
00:35:38,480 --> 00:35:40,110
She threw up.

798
00:35:41,650 --> 00:35:42,180
Threw up?

799
00:35:45,790 --> 00:35:47,660
But this dish smells really good.

800
00:35:48,840 --> 00:35:49,440
Let me try.

801
00:35:59,760 --> 00:36:00,760
It's pretty good.

802
00:36:03,710 --> 00:36:05,030
She threw up?

803
00:37:01,010 --> 00:37:02,760
What's wrong?

804
00:37:02,820 --> 00:37:04,150
Are you feeling unwell?

805
00:37:05,460 --> 00:37:06,630
Something's with Ranran.

806
00:37:06,630 --> 00:37:08,320
That's not how you throw up
when you're sick.

807
00:37:08,320 --> 00:37:13,030
I was pregnant with Xiaobao, I know.

808
00:37:16,170 --> 00:37:17,340
You mean

809
00:37:18,480 --> 00:37:19,210
Ranran is...

810
00:37:19,340 --> 00:37:19,940
Pregnant?

811
00:37:24,440 --> 00:37:25,210
Chu Caiyuan!

812
00:37:25,230 --> 00:37:26,840
-Get out of the car!
-You again?

813
00:37:26,840 --> 00:37:27,850
Get out of the car!

814
00:37:27,920 --> 00:37:28,340
Are you ever going to stop?

815
00:37:28,340 --> 00:37:28,860
Security!

816
00:37:28,860 --> 00:37:29,860
Get out of the car!

817
00:37:30,480 --> 00:37:31,810
Won't you give it a rest?

818
00:37:31,900 --> 00:37:34,460
Get out, you scumbag!

819
00:37:34,760 --> 00:37:35,650
Don't talk nonsense.

820
00:37:35,650 --> 00:37:36,560
He knows

821
00:37:36,590 --> 00:37:37,870
what he did.

822
00:37:38,190 --> 00:37:40,350
You ruined a girl's life!

823
00:37:40,510 --> 00:37:41,550
You scumbag!

824
00:37:41,550 --> 00:37:42,560
Get out of the car!

825
00:37:43,320 --> 00:37:44,230
Get out!

826
00:37:45,210 --> 00:37:46,570
Get out!

827
00:38:05,480 --> 00:38:06,320
Mr. Guo.

828
00:38:07,650 --> 00:38:08,230
Mr. Guo.

829
00:38:10,800 --> 00:38:11,400
What's up?

830
00:38:12,070 --> 00:38:13,400
Northeasterner told me you got hurt.

831
00:38:13,400 --> 00:38:14,210
What happened?

832
00:38:14,210 --> 00:38:14,890
I'm fine.

833
00:38:14,920 --> 00:38:16,230
I was working

834
00:38:16,230 --> 00:38:17,570
and accidentally

835
00:38:17,900 --> 00:38:19,430
pulled my back.

836
00:38:21,420 --> 00:38:22,220
It's nothing.

837
00:38:24,360 --> 00:38:25,890
What happened to your face?

838
00:38:26,010 --> 00:38:26,610
I- I...

839
00:38:26,780 --> 00:38:29,130
I just took a fall.

840
00:38:36,210 --> 00:38:37,180
It's nothing.

841
00:38:39,030 --> 00:38:40,570
Did you go find Chu Caiyuan?

842
00:38:46,550 --> 00:38:48,260
I just couldn't stand it.

843
00:38:49,190 --> 00:38:52,500
How could he bully you like this?

844
00:38:55,480 --> 00:38:57,400
It's nothing.

845
00:38:58,050 --> 00:38:59,260
I'm fine.

846
00:39:06,500 --> 00:39:07,890
Where else are you hurt? Let me see.

847
00:39:07,890 --> 00:39:09,420
I'm fine. I'm really fine.

848
00:39:19,420 --> 00:39:20,350
I'll go find him.

849
00:39:20,710 --> 00:39:21,310
Ranran,

850
00:39:21,760 --> 00:39:22,840
don't go.

851
00:39:24,590 --> 00:39:25,610
If you go,

852
00:39:26,280 --> 00:39:28,740
I would have taken
this beating for nothing.

853
00:39:29,280 --> 00:39:29,960
Right?

854
00:39:30,460 --> 00:39:31,490
I went to see him

855
00:39:32,190 --> 00:39:33,930
because I didn't want

856
00:39:34,530 --> 00:39:36,530
him to harass you

857
00:39:36,550 --> 00:39:37,780
or see you again.

858
00:39:40,640 --> 00:39:42,100
Then I'll call the police.

859
00:39:42,880 --> 00:39:44,280
No, no, you can't.

860
00:39:46,190 --> 00:39:47,190
This matter

861
00:39:51,730 --> 00:39:53,660
cannot be blown out of proportion.

862
00:39:58,070 --> 00:40:00,860
Come, sit with me for a while.

863
00:40:14,170 --> 00:40:15,090
About this,

864
00:40:16,400 --> 00:40:19,980
don't tell your aunt.

865
00:40:21,440 --> 00:40:24,110
Don't mention it to Xiaobao either.

866
00:40:31,940 --> 00:40:32,400
Mr. Guo,

867
00:40:36,900 --> 00:40:37,990
I feel so wronged.

868
00:40:41,570 --> 00:40:43,020
It's okay, girl.

869
00:40:45,690 --> 00:40:50,960
Let's sit and get some air.

870
00:40:59,590 --> 00:41:00,650
Get some fresh air.

871
00:41:05,340 --> 00:41:05,840
Wang,

872
00:41:06,360 --> 00:41:08,670
make sure these workers
eat and drink well.

873
00:41:08,670 --> 00:41:09,340
Take good care of them.

874
00:41:09,340 --> 00:41:09,650
Okay.

875
00:41:09,650 --> 00:41:10,280
Go quickly.

876
00:41:10,280 --> 00:41:11,610
Don't worry, Director.

877
00:41:19,640 --> 00:41:20,510
Yang,

878
00:41:20,820 --> 00:41:21,480
what's wrong?

879
00:41:21,480 --> 00:41:22,780
We are about to return to Beijing.

880
00:41:22,780 --> 00:41:24,860
We need to hurry back and find workers.

881
00:41:24,860 --> 00:41:25,660
What workers?

882
00:41:26,070 --> 00:41:27,790
Aren't all the workers here?

883
00:41:28,260 --> 00:41:29,030
They are?

884
00:41:29,860 --> 00:41:31,980
Ye called me yesterday.

885
00:41:32,530 --> 00:41:34,820
He said it was about your business.

886
00:41:35,030 --> 00:41:35,960
I thought, "Wow,

887
00:41:36,070 --> 00:41:37,840
what a small world."

888
00:41:38,050 --> 00:41:39,150
Yay? What "Yay"?

889
00:41:40,190 --> 00:41:41,130
Not yay.

890
00:41:41,440 --> 00:41:42,000
Ye.

891
00:41:42,000 --> 00:41:43,360
Ye from Cotton Mill No. 2.

892
00:41:43,360 --> 00:41:43,920
He said his daughter

893
00:41:43,920 --> 00:41:45,380
is your friend in Beijing.

894
00:41:47,000 --> 00:41:48,260
Zhuang Zhuang, right?

895
00:41:48,760 --> 00:41:49,690
That's not Ye.

896
00:41:49,690 --> 00:41:51,000
That's your father-in-law.

897
00:41:51,000 --> 00:41:51,610
What father-in-law?

898
00:41:51,610 --> 00:41:52,610
Don't talk nonsense.

899
00:41:52,610 --> 00:41:54,070
Ye really is capable.

900
00:41:54,940 --> 00:41:55,590
He got all these workers

901
00:41:55,590 --> 00:41:56,550
back here.

902
00:41:57,070 --> 00:41:58,270
Now that we have them,

903
00:41:58,630 --> 00:42:00,610
our factory can take orders again.

904
00:42:01,070 --> 00:42:01,640
Yes.

905
00:42:01,780 --> 00:42:03,090
That's great.

906
00:42:04,070 --> 00:42:04,600
Shengli,

907
00:42:05,380 --> 00:42:06,630
about what you said last time,

908
00:42:06,630 --> 00:42:08,290
I thought about it carefully.

909
00:42:08,500 --> 00:42:09,960
Now that all the workers are here,

910
00:42:09,960 --> 00:42:11,220
I feel more confident.

911
00:42:11,710 --> 00:42:12,320
You don't need to

912
00:42:12,320 --> 00:42:14,120
pay the 50,000 deposit anymore.

913
00:42:14,280 --> 00:42:15,810
You have 30,000,

914
00:42:16,150 --> 00:42:17,110
and you're

915
00:42:17,130 --> 00:42:18,050
a Beijing man who has

916
00:42:18,050 --> 00:42:18,910
been to Russia.

917
00:42:18,940 --> 00:42:20,630
Ensure the quality of the leather for me.

918
00:42:20,630 --> 00:42:21,860
Once the machines are fixed,

919
00:42:21,860 --> 00:42:23,590
we will start full production.

920
00:42:24,480 --> 00:42:26,400
You still want 30,000
despite being confident?

921
00:42:26,400 --> 00:42:27,130
Don't worry.

922
00:42:27,190 --> 00:42:28,440
I will definitely
deliver the deposit and leather

923
00:42:28,440 --> 00:42:29,570
to you on time.

924
00:42:29,860 --> 00:42:30,790
B-Brother Yang.

925
00:42:31,000 --> 00:42:33,130
Although our order is small this time,

926
00:42:33,130 --> 00:42:34,730
we must ensure both quality and quantity.

927
00:42:34,730 --> 00:42:35,880
We are going to export them.

928
00:42:35,880 --> 00:42:37,610
Every product of ours represents

929
00:42:37,610 --> 00:42:39,050
China's international image.

930
00:42:39,050 --> 00:42:40,300
Oh my, those words

931
00:42:40,320 --> 00:42:41,380
got me all fired up.

932
00:42:41,500 --> 00:42:42,130
Shengli,

933
00:42:42,360 --> 00:42:43,610
you don't know well enough

934
00:42:43,610 --> 00:42:44,940
what kind of person I am.

935
00:42:45,130 --> 00:42:46,000
The quality of the product

936
00:42:46,000 --> 00:42:46,930
is our lifeline.

937
00:42:47,440 --> 00:42:48,530
I will definitely do a good job.

938
00:42:48,530 --> 00:42:49,550
You can rest assured.

939
00:42:49,550 --> 00:42:50,360
How about this?

940
00:42:50,360 --> 00:42:51,570
Let's meet the workers

941
00:42:51,570 --> 00:42:52,440
and encourage them.

942
00:42:52,440 --> 00:42:52,820
Okay?

943
00:42:52,940 --> 00:42:53,340
Hurry.

944
00:42:53,630 --> 00:42:54,230
Come here.

945
00:42:54,320 --> 00:42:55,110
-Well…
-Come in.

946
00:42:55,110 --> 00:42:56,370
-Come on.
-Now you’ve got me stumped.
